[{"type":"warning","header":"如果报 'CDK synth failed: ... uv install failed ... exit code null'","html":"<p>SSM session 超时重连之后,新 shell 的 PATH 没把 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">~/.local/bin</code> 带上,而 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">uv</code>(打包 evaluator Lambda 用)就装在那里——deploy 找不到 uv 就崩。一句话修好:</p><div class=\"CodeBlock-module_codeBlock__LKx5X CodeBlock-module_hasCopyAction__WMrpt\"><pre dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: black; font-family: var(--font-family-monospace-q47m7k, Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier Prime', Courier, 'Courier New', monospace); font-size: 13px; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; box-sizing: border-box;\"><code class=\"language-bash\" style=\"white-space: pre; color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><code style=\"color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; float: left; padding-right: var(--space-scaled-xl-gt502a, 24px);\"><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">1\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">2\n</span><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">3\n</span></code><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">export</span><span> </span><span class=\"token assign-left environment\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 85);\">PATH</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">=</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">\"</span><span class=\"token environment\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 85);\">$HOME</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">/.local/bin:</span><span class=\"token environment\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 85);\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">\"</span><span>\n</span><span></span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 74, 104);\">which</span><span> uv </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(154, 110, 58);\">&amp;&amp;</span><span> uv --version    </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: slategray;\"># 确认能找到</span><span>\n</span><span>agentcore deploy --yes      </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: slategray;\"># 重跑</span></code></pre><span class=\"awsui_root_xjuzf_11ym3_559 CodeBlock-module_copyAction__E7A8w\"><span class=\"awsui_trigger_xjuzf_11ym3_594\" id=\":r2n:\"><button class=\"CopyButton-module_styledButton__sS63U awsui_button_vjswe_1ufnn_157 awsui_variant-normal_vjswe_1ufnn_206 awsui_button-no-text_vjswe_1ufnn_601\" data-testid=\"copy-button\" aria-label=\"Copy content\" title=\"Copy content\" data-analytics-funnel-value=\"button:r2o:\" type=\"submit\" data-analytics-performance-mark=\"7-1782459597477-8130\"><span class=\"awsui_icon_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon-left_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon_h11ix_3ufhe_189 awsui_size-normal-mapped-height_h11ix_3ufhe_248 awsui_size-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_244 awsui_variant-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_320\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 5H5v10h10V5Z\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path><path d=\"M13 1H1v11\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path></svg></span></button></span></span></div><p>修一次只对当前 shell 有效。如果你后面又重连了 SSM,记得再 export 一次,或写进 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">~/.bashrc</code> 一劳永逸:<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">echo 'export PATH=$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH' &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc</code>。</p>"},{"type":"warning","header":"","html":"<p><code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">--actor-id</code> 必填（Harness 用它读取该用户的 Memory）。取值要符合 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">[a-zA-Z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9-_/]*</code>——别用冒号，否则底层 <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">ListEvents</code> 调用会校验失败。</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"","html":"<p>保持问题文本一致是公平对比的前提——只改了 Prompt 这一个变量，才能把分数变化归因到 Prompt 优化。这就是受控实验的思路。</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"","html":"<p><strong>一键完成整个 Phase 5</strong>：<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">10-optimize-prompt.sh</code> 把本节（写优化 Prompt → 部署 → 重新跑三个问题）和 5.2（重新评估）打包好了——写入抗幻觉 Prompt、重新部署、用相同三个问题重对话、再评估并打印分数，整段自动跑完。下面的命令用于手动理解每一步在做什么。</p><div class=\"CodeBlock-module_codeBlock__LKx5X CodeBlock-module_hasCopyAction__WMrpt\"><pre dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: black; font-family: var(--font-family-monospace-q47m7k, Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier Prime', Courier, 'Courier New', monospace); font-size: 13px; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; box-sizing: border-box;\"><code class=\"language-bash\" style=\"white-space: pre; color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><code style=\"color: black; background: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: inherit; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; float: left; padding-right: var(--space-scaled-xl-gt502a, 24px);\"><span class=\"react-syntax-highlighter-line-number\" style=\"opacity: 0.38;\">1\n</span></code><span>./10-optimize-prompt.sh</span></code></pre><span class=\"awsui_root_xjuzf_11ym3_559 CodeBlock-module_copyAction__E7A8w\"><span class=\"awsui_trigger_xjuzf_11ym3_594\" id=\":r33:\"><button class=\"CopyButton-module_styledButton__sS63U awsui_button_vjswe_1ufnn_157 awsui_variant-normal_vjswe_1ufnn_206 awsui_button-no-text_vjswe_1ufnn_601\" data-testid=\"copy-button\" aria-label=\"Copy content\" title=\"Copy content\" data-analytics-funnel-value=\"button:r34:\" type=\"submit\" data-analytics-performance-mark=\"9-1782459597485-478\"><span class=\"awsui_icon_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon-left_vjswe_1ufnn_630 awsui_icon_h11ix_3ufhe_189 awsui_size-normal-mapped-height_h11ix_3ufhe_248 awsui_size-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_244 awsui_variant-normal_h11ix_3ufhe_320\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 5H5v10h10V5Z\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path><path d=\"M13 1H1v11\" class=\"stroke-linejoin-round\"></path></svg></span></button></span></span></div>"},{"type":"success","header":"","html":"<p>新 Prompt 已部署，三个问题也用相同文本重新跑了一遍，新 trace 已经生成。你现在手里有\"优化前\"和\"优化后\"两套数据——下一节用同一套评估器对比分数，看改动到底有没有用。</p>"}]